OL,3,CSuspicious object found in east Belfast
OL,5,FPolice are currently examining a
OL,6,Fsuspicious object in the Orangefield
OL,7,FPark area of east Belfast.
OL,9,FA number of cordons have been put in
OL,10,Fplace inside the park on Wednesday
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,13,FOfficers have asked members of the
OL,14,Fpublic to avoid the area.
OL,16,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,17,Fhere.
